name: COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania, Respondent v. David SNYDER, Petitioner

opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 10th day of December, 2009, the Petition for Leave to File a Petition for Allowance of Appeal Nunc Pro Tunc is GRANTED. Counsel is directed to file a Petition for Allowance of Appeal within 30 days of our order.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
